    "about.legal.body" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "NOT AN OFFICIAL MINECRAFT PRODUCT. NOT APPROVED BY OR ASSOCIATED WITH MOJANG OR MICROSOFT.\n\nCouchMC is an unofficial third-party touch-controller utility. References to “Minecraft” are nominative — used only to describe what game CouchMC is compatible with — and do not imply any partnership, sponsorship, endorsement, or affiliation with Mojang Studios, Mojang AB, Mojang Synergies AB, Microsoft Corporation, or Notch Development AB.\n\nMINECRAFT, MOJANG, and the Minecraft and Mojang logos are trademarks or registered trademarks of Mojang Synergies AB or its affiliates. Microsoft and Windows are trademarks of Microsoft Corporation. Apple, iPhone, iPad, macOS, and iOS are trademarks of Apple Inc. All other product and company names referenced in this app are trademarks of their respective holders.\n\nThe game itself is not bundled with this app. Players must own a separate, valid copy of Minecraft Java Edition installed on their own PC."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "本 App 并非 Minecraft 官方产品，未获得 Mojang 或 Microsoft 的认可，与之亦无任何关联。\n\nCouchMC 是非官方第三方触屏控制器工具。文中出现的「Minecraft」属于指示性使用——仅为说明本 App 兼容哪款游戏，并不暗示与 Mojang Studios、Mojang AB、Mojang Synergies AB、Microsoft Corporation 或 Notch Development AB 之间存在任何合作、赞助、授权或隶属关系。\n\nMINECRAFT、MOJANG 以及 Minecraft 与 Mojang 的相关标识，均为 Mojang Synergies AB 或其关联公司之商标或注册商标。Microsoft 与 Windows 为 Microsoft Corporation 之商标。Apple、iPhone、iPad、macOS 与 iOS 为 Apple Inc. 之商标。文中其他产品与公司名称均为各自所有者之商标。\n\n本 App 不包含游戏本体。使用者须自行在 PC 上拥有合法授权的 Minecraft Java 版。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
