            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "While dragging a widget in the layout editor, a grey dashed line appears when its edge or centre is about to align with another widget's, and amber arrows mark equal spacing. After selecting a widget you can also swipe on empty canvas to fine-tune position (axis-locked, slower than your finger)."
